{"tid":1268674,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚多on9仔話7月1要升黑旗","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T11:48:52.000Z","uid":16184,"like":15,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e2a43484ab6f04cc1a3b4e62a62af0fb026b22","tid":1268674,"uid":16184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"升旗之前用下腦，睇下書，唔好亂鳩咁升旗： <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑旗的政治含意： </span><br />\nBlack flags have traditionally been flown by anarchism, and left-wing radicals to represent the absence of all oppressive structures. A combination of the two colors in a black flag represents social anarchism, such as anarchist communism and anarcho syndicalism.<br />\n簡單講，黑旗代表無政府主義，要推翻現行既整個政府，意思即係<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 發動政變</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果大家只係想哀悼我地既義人，可以升返香港旗 下半旗已經可以，唔需要升黑旗。<br />\n黑旗仲有另一個層面既意思：<br />\nWhat does raise the black flag mean?<br />\nIt means to give no quater or kill everyone. It comes from pirates raising a black flag then taking no prisoners after the attack. The quote, from Mencken's 1919 Prejudices (First Series), is in full: &quot;Every normal man must be tempted, at times, to spit upon his hands, hoist the black flag, and begin slitting throats.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n意思係 殺無赦，任何人都要殺，只要唔同意我地立場既人都要死，係一種接近恐怖主義既思想同行動。<br />\n<br />\n[<span style=\"color: red;\">b]所以，唔該你班on9仔，學生獨立聯盟，唔好做埋D會推全香港去死既行為。[/b]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地只需要下半旗，唔需要升黑旗，做恐怖分子。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4a9da8ac8ccdcb0851195900e9d80ffc5f882e94","tid":1268674,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"升林鄭既車頭相上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0bc4fcb67a2d84673eb3927bb1a85239c4df8c","tid":1268674,"uid":20115,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma